# B2B Fabric Company Landing Page

A high-performance, SEO-optimized landing page for a B2B fabric company built with [Next.js](https://nextjs.org/).  
**No client-side JavaScript** is shipped for a lightning-fast and accessible user experience.

---

## 🚀 Features

- **Zero client-side JavaScript** – Pure SSR/SSG HTML.
- **SEO optimized** for high Google rankings (structured data, meta tags, schema, fast load).
- **B2B focused design** for fabric/textile companies.
- **Accessible & mobile-first** layout.
- **Fast loading** with image optimization and minimal resources.
- **Inspired by:** [dhananjaycreation.com/ahmedabad/embroidered-sarees.htm](https://dhananjaycreation.com/ahmedabad/embroidered-sarees.htm)

---

## 📸 Demo

