---

## 🏗️ Project Structure

- `pages/` - All static pages (SSR/SSG).
- `public/` - Images and static assets.
- `components/` - Reusable UI elements (all server-rendered).
- `styles/` - CSS modules or global styles, with critical CSS.

---

## 🔍 SEO Approach

- Clean, semantic HTML (using Next.js server-side features).
- Custom `<Head>` tags for each page with meta descriptions, titles, and Open Graph.
- Image `alt` attributes for accessibility and SEO.
- [Schema.org](https://schema.org/) markup for products/services.
- Fast load time (Google Core Web Vitals).
- No client-side JS = No hydration or unnecessary JS files.

---

## 💼 B2B Focused Elements

- Product categories and service sections tailored for fabric wholesalers and buyers.
- Strong CTAs: "Request Quote," "Contact Us," "View Catalogue."
- Trust signals: Certifications, client logos, testimonials, etc.
- Clear contact and location info.

---

